  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Drawing on the deepest fears of a group of creatures, you create illusory creatures in their minds, visible only to them. Each creature in a 30-foot-radius sphere centered on a point of your choice within range must make an <strong>Intelligence saving throw</strong>. On a failed save, a creature becomes frightened for the duration. The illusion calls on the creature's deepest fears, manifesting its worst nightmares as an implacable threat. At the end of each of the frightened creature's turns, it takes <strong>8d10 psychic damage</strong> and must succeed on an <strong>Intelligence saving throw</strong>. On a successful save, the spell ends for that creature.</p>",
